See?

33
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,340
We’re hilarious.

34
00:01:23,340 --> 00:01:25,400
Pence also said the Chinese regime is trying
to

35
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:28,440
undermine democracy in the United States.

36
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:32,460
Worst of all, China has initiated an unprecedented
effort

37
00:01:32,470 --> 00:01:35,680
to influence American public opinion,

38
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,860
the 2018 elections,

39
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:39,220
and the environment leading into

40
00:01:39,220 --> 00:01:41,420
the 2020 presidential elections…

41
00:01:41,420 --> 00:01:43,610
Now that’s something President Trump

42
00:01:43,610 --> 00:01:46,570
