43
00:01:46,570 --> 00:01:48,229
If you haven’t been paying attention,

44
00:01:48,229 --> 00:01:51,360
some of Pence’s speech might seem a little
exaggerated.

45
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:53,329
The Chinese Communist Party is rewarding

46
00:01:53,329 --> 00:01:55,200
or coercing American businesses,

47
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:58,720
movie studios, universities, think tanks,

48
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:02,890
