federal officials.

49
00:02:02,890 --> 00:02:06,840
I mean, that is a lot of people to reward
or coerce.

50
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:08,979
But as the Wall Street Journal puts it,

51
00:02:08,979 --> 00:02:10,700
