55
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:22,569
power and rewards to affect the way it is
viewed in the US.”

56
00:02:22,569 --> 00:02:23,980
As I’m sure you can imagine,

57
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:26,150
the Chinese Communist Party was not happy
about

58
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:28,900
Pence spreading all these malicious rumors

59
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:32,230
to undermine China’s harmonious society.

60
00:02:32,230 --> 00:02:36,240
Which is why state-run Xinhua ran this article
called,

61
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,950
“Not-so-Bright Rumor-Spreading:

62
00:02:37,950 --> 00:02:43,209
