78
00:03:18,770 --> 00:03:22,020
It’s a search engine that would censor all
the things

79
00:03:22,020 --> 00:03:25,700
the Chinese Communist Party doesn’t want
people to know about.

80
00:03:25,700 --> 00:03:28,360
Pence even mentioned it in his speech.

81
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,750
For example,

82
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:33,970
Google should immediately end development
of the “Dragonfly” app

83
00:03:33,970 --> 00:03:37,019
