the BBC,

88
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:54,769
“Right now all we’ve done is some exploration,

89
00:03:54,769 --> 00:03:57,189
but since we don't have any plans to launch
something

90
00:03:57,189 --> 00:03:59,409
